attributionInfo.brokerName: Better Homes and Gardens Real Estate Treasure II
Better Homes and Gardens Real Estate Treasure II

data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This delightful residence boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a bonus room, offering a perfect blend of comfort and style on an expansive half-acre lot. Situated in a desirable no HOA community with no city taxes, this home is a rare find, providing a short drive to the award-winning Topsail Beaches, shopping, and military bases.Inside, the open-concept living area welcomes you with vaulted ceilings, featuring 3-inch engineered hardwood floors and a gas-burning fireplace for cozy gatherings. The well-appointed kitchen showcases Frigidaire appliances, a 5-burner smooth top stove, staggered cabinets, and a two-tiered eat-in breakfast area. Split floor plan offers retreat like experience with isolated Master Suite, complete with vaulted ceilings and a large walk-in closet. Enjoy outdoor living on the covered front porch or back patio, surrounded by a fenced backyard providing privacy and a safe play area. Exterior features, including stacked stone accents, add to the home's curb appeal. Additional highlights include a laundry room conveniently located off the 2 car garage.Don't miss the chance to experience the charm and functionality of this beautiful home, schedule a showing today!
